Upgrade Proposal: Bedrock - This proposal outlines the Optimism Collective’s first Protocol upgrade of Optimism Mainnet to the Bedrock release. This upgrade aims to provide unprecedented modularity, simplicity, and Ethereum equivalence to the L2 network, with positive impacts on performance and security. Bedrock is the codebase which will help Optimism stand the test of time, and is also preparatory step towards the multi-chain future. - This Protocol Upgrade proposal is eligible for voting in Voting Cycle #11: https://gov.optimism.io/t/final-upgrade-proposal-bedrock-v2/5548

Delegate Suspension: Fractal Visions - All Optimism Delegates are bound by the delegate code of conduct (https://gov.optimism.io/t/delegate-code-of-conduct/3943.) Severe code of conduct violations are subject to a three month suspension and are decided via Token House vote. - This Delegate Suspension Proposal is eligible for voting in Voting Cycle #11: https://gov.optimism.io/t/delegate-suspension-fractal-visions/5710 // Note: the approval threshold for this proposal is 51%, or 20424975 OP.
